skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: forest bird sounds
des:
Let the sounds of these forest birds put you in a deep sleep. Forest Bird Sounds is the ultimate science-backed companion for relaxation, focus, and better sleep. 

All you need to do is say Alexa start Forest Bird Sounds, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to leave on while you are asleep, to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
